---
// TextToVector.astro — Visual showing how text becomes an embedding vector
---

<div class="ttv-wrap">
  <h3 class="ttv-title">From Text to Numbers — How Embedding Works</h3>
  <p class="ttv-sub">A sentence goes in. A list of numbers comes out. Those numbers capture meaning.</p>

  <div class="ttv-flow">
    <div class="ttv-step ttv-step--1">
      <div class="ttv-step-label">Input Text</div>
      <div class="ttv-text-box">
        <span class="ttv-quote">"The cat sat on the mat"</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-arrow ttv-arrow--1">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 50 20"><path d="M5 10h35M35 4l8 6-8 6" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-step ttv-step--2">
      <div class="ttv-step-label">Tokenization</div>
      <div class="ttv-tokens">
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--1">The</span>
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--2">cat</span>
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--3">sat</span>
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--4">on</span>
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--5">the</span>
        <span class="ttv-token ttv-tok--6">mat</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-arrow ttv-arrow--2">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 50 20"><path d="M5 10h35M35 4l8 6-8 6" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-step ttv-step--3">
      <div class="ttv-step-label">Embedding Model</div>
      <div class="ttv-model-box">
        <div class="ttv-model-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#818cf8" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M8 7h8M8 12h8M8 17h4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="ttv-model-name">text-embedding-3-small</span>
        <span class="ttv-model-detail">1,536 dimensions</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-arrow ttv-arrow--3">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 50 20"><path d="M5 10h35M35 4l8 6-8 6" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="ttv-step ttv-step--4">
      <div class="ttv-step-label">Vector Output</div>
      <div class="ttv-vector-box">
        <div class="ttv-vector-row">
          <span class="ttv-dim">[0]</span><div class="ttv-bar-track"><div class="ttv-vbar" style="--w:72%;--c:#4ade80"></div></div><span class="ttv-vval">0.0234</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ttv-vector-row">
          <span class="ttv-dim">[1]</span><div class="ttv-bar-track"><div class="ttv-vbar" style="--w:45%;--c:#06b6d4"></div></div><span class="ttv-vval">-0.0891</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ttv-vector-row">
          <span class="ttv-dim">[2]</span><div class="ttv-bar-track"><div class="ttv-vbar" style="--w:88%;--c:#818cf8"></div></div><span class="ttv-vval">0.1472</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ttv-vector-row">
          <span class="ttv-dim">[3]</span><div class="ttv-bar-track"><div class="ttv-vbar" style="--w:30%;--c:#f59e0b"></div></div><span class="ttv-vval">-0.0156</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ttv-ellipsis">... 1,532 more dimensions</div>
        <div class="ttv-vector-row">
          <span class="ttv-dim">[1535]</span><div class="ttv-bar-track"><div class="ttv-vbar" style="--w:60%;--c:#f472b6"></div></div><span class="ttv-vval">0.0672</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ttv-insight">
    Each number captures a different aspect of meaning — tone, topic, syntax, entities. You can't read a single dimension, but **the whole vector is a fingerprint of the sentence's meaning**.
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .ttv-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .ttv-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .ttv-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .ttv-flow {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; min-width: 800px; padding: 8px 0;
  }

  .ttv-step { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .ttv-step-label { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: monospace; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  .ttv-step--1, .ttv-step--2, .ttv-step--3, .ttv-step--4 {
    opacity: 0; animation: ttvIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .ttv-step--1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .ttv-step--2 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .ttv-step--3 { animation-delay: 0.9s; }
  .ttv-step--4 { animation-delay: 1.3s; }

  .ttv-text-box {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px;
  }
  .ttv-quote { color: #4ade80; font-size: 0.75rem; font-style: italic; }

  .ttv-tokens { display: flex; gap: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ttv-token {
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;
    opacity: 0; animation: ttvTokIn 0.3s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .ttv-tok--1 { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .ttv-tok--2 { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.12); color: #06b6d4; animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .ttv-tok--3 { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.12); color: #818cf8; animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .ttv-tok--4 { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: #f59e0b; animation-delay: 0.9s; }
  .ttv-tok--5 { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; animation-delay: 1.0s; }
  .ttv-tok--6 { background: rgba(244,114,182,0.12); color: #f472b6; animation-delay: 1.1s; }

  .ttv-model-box {
    background: rgba(129,140,248,0.06); border: 1px solid #818cf830; border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px; text-align: center;
  }
  .ttv-model-icon { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .ttv-model-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; margin: 0 auto; display: block; }
  .ttv-model-name { display: block; color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 0.65rem; font-family: monospace; font-weight: 700; }
  .ttv-model-detail { display: block; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.5rem; font-family: monospace; margin-top: 2px; }

  .ttv-vector-box {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; min-width: 180px;
  }
  .ttv-vector-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .ttv-dim { color: #475569; font-size: 0.5rem; font-family: monospace; min-width: 36px; text-align: right; }
  .ttv-bar-track { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .ttv-vbar { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; width: 0; animation: ttvBarGrow 1s ease-out 1.5s forwards; background: var(--c); }
  .ttv-vval { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.5rem; font-family: monospace; min-width: 48px; }
  .ttv-ellipsis { color: #475569; font-size: 0.5rem; font-family: monospace; text-align: center; padding: 4px 0; }

  .ttv-arrow { flex: 0 0 50px; display: flex; align-items: center; opacity: 0; animation: ttvIn 0.3s ease-out forwards; }
  .ttv-arrow--1 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .ttv-arrow--2 { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .ttv-arrow--3 { animation-delay: 1.1s; }

  .ttv-insight {
    margin-top: 16px; padding: 12px 14px; border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(6,182,212,0.05); border: 1px solid #06b6d420;
    color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .ttv-insight strong { color: #67e8f9; }

  @keyframes ttvIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes ttvTokIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }
  @keyframes ttvBarGrow { to { width: var(--w); } }
</style>
